  <summary date="2020-03-13T14:59:40Z" status="Introduced in House">Health Care Workforce Protection Act of 2019

This bill extends targeted liability protection to certain manufacturers, distributors, prescribers, and users of approved respiratory protective devices that are used under certain conditions during a declared public health emergency.</summary>
